name: James H. WILLIAMS, Petitioner v. Hon. Sheila WOODS-SKIPPER (Judiciary Officer for Court of Common Pleas of Phila. Pa.), Respondent

opinions.text:
ORDER
PER CURIAM.
AND NOW, this 11th day of August, 2014, the Petition for Writ of Mandamus is DENIED. The Prothonotary is directed to strike the name of the jurist from the caption.
opinions.author: PER CURIAM.
